s_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/34350","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/34350","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/34350.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/34350.patch","merged_at":"2020-01-17T07:39:59Z"},"body":"Fixes #34348.

Seems to be about 2x faster than pivoted QR for a large underdetermined solve, with similar accuracy (assuming full row rank):
```jl
julia> A = rand(1000,1500); b = rand(size(A,1));

julia> @btime lq($A) \ $b;
  101.955 ms (14 allocations: 19.37 MiB)

julia> @btime qr($A, Val{true}()) \ $b;
  250.584 ms (8046 allocations: 31.98 MiB)

julia> x = lq(A) \ b; norm(x - qr(A, Val{true}()) \ b) / norm(x)
3.5357944054772334e-15
